data.description: Welcome to 6557 Yellow Hill Dr, in the charming town of Milton, FL. Step inside and be captivated by the spacious open-concept design, featuring soaring ceilings and abundant natural light that fills every corner. The thoughtfully designed layout boasts a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it an entertainer's paradise. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the kitchen. Lots of counter and cabinet space with a large pantry. The home also has a water purification system. Retreat to the cozy primary suite for relaxation and enjoy the large spa like bath, double vanity and walk in closet.Two additional spacious bedrooms provide comfort and privacy for family members or guests.The outdoor space is equally enchanting, featuring a large deck, fenced backyard perfect for gatherings and playtime. 6557 Yellow Hill Dr is conveniently located close to excellent schools, parks, shopping, and dining, ensuring you have everything you need at your fingertips. NAS Whiting field, Whiting Pines Mini Mart, Navarre Beach and Blackwater river are also closely located. The neighborhood is quiet and offers a great place for a evening walk. Water heater 2020, HVAC 2020, New Roof and Gutters 2023
